videos.description: Chase Garbers keeps the ball and pounds his way through the TCU defense to score the first touchdown of the night for Cal.
videos.headline: Garbers pounds way to Cal TD

videos.description: Sewo Olonilua navigates his way 14 yards to the end zone for a TCU touchdown to tie Cal, but it ends up getting called back.
videos.headline: Key TCU fourth down conversion sets up TD

videos.description: Sewo Olonilua powers his way through the Cal defense to finally reach the end zone after stretching out.
videos.headline: Olonilua fights his way for TCU TD

videos.description: TCU seals a comeback victory with an overtime field goal to defeat Cal 10-7.
videos.headline: TCU wins with overtime field goal
